Stick the following in your .screenrc:
----- start -----
#More Xterm Color Hacks
 termcap  vt100 'AF=\E[3%dm:AB=\E[4%dm'
 terminfo vt100 'AF=\E[3%p1%dm:AB=\E[4%p1%dm'
 termcap  vs100 AF=\E[3%dm
 terminfo vs100 AF=\E[3%p1%dm
 termcap  vs100 AB=\E[4%dm
 terminfo vs100 AB=\E[4%p1%dm
----- end -----

I don't know who originally posted this, but it works like a charm.

